<p><span class="vocab">教師<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教師</rb><rt>きょうし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;instructors</span></span>も<span class="vocab">生徒<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生徒</rb><rt>せいと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;students</span></span>も<span class="vocab">帰って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;return home</span></span>しまったあとで、<span class="vocab">一人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一人</rb><rt>ひとり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;alone; by oneself</span></span><span class="vocab">ぽかんと<span class="vocabdef">ぽかんと&nbsp;vacantly; blankly; like a fool</span></span>しているのは<span class="vocab">随分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>随分</rb><rt>ずいぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;very much; terribly</span></span><span class="vocab">間が抜けた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>間</rb><rt>ま</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>抜</rb><rt>ぬ</rt></ruby>けた&nbsp;stupid; out of place</span></span>ものだ。<span class="vocab">宿直部屋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿直部屋</rb><rt>しゅくちょくべや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;night duty room</span></span>は<span class="vocab">教場<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教場</rb><rt>きょうじょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;classrooms</span></span>の<span class="vocab">裏手<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>裏手</rb><rt>うらて</rt></ruby>&nbsp;back side; behind</span></span>にある<span class="vocab">寄宿舎<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寄宿舎</rb><rt>きしゅくしゃ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dormitory</span></span>の<span class="vocab">西はずれ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>西</rb><rt>にし</rt></ruby>はずれ&nbsp;west end</span></span>の<span class="vocab">一室<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一室</rb><rt>いっしつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;single room</span></span>だ。ちょっとはいってみたが、<span class="vocab">西日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>西日</rb><rt>にしび</rt></ruby>&nbsp;setting sun (lit: western sun)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">まともに<span class="vocabdef">まともに&nbsp;directly</span></span><span class="vocab">受けて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>受</rb><rt>う</rt></ruby>けて&nbsp;receive</span></span>、<span class="vocab">苦しくって<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>苦</rb><rt>くる</rt></ruby>しくって&nbsp;excruciating</span></span><span class="vocab">居たたまれない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>たたまれない&nbsp;cannot bear to stay</span></span>。<span class="vocab">田舎<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>田舎</rb><rt>いなか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the country</span></span><span class="vocab">だけあって<span class="vocabdef">だけあって&nbsp;as expected of</span></span><span class="vocab">秋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>秋</rb><rt>あき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;autumn</span></span>がきても、<span class="vocab">気長に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気長</rb><rt>きなが</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;persistently; in no hurry (to change)</span></span><span class="vocab">暑い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>暑</rb><rt>あつ</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;hot</span></span>もんだ。生徒の<span class="vocab">賄<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>賄</rb><rt>まかない</rt></ruby>&nbsp;board (dormitory meals)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">取りよせて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>取</rb><rt>と</rt></ruby>りよせて&nbsp;send for</span></span><span class="vocab">晩飯<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>晩飯</rb><rt>ばんめし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;evening meal</span></span>を<span class="vocab">済ました<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>済</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>ました&nbsp;finished</span></span>が、まずいには<span class="vocab">恐れ入った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>恐</rb><rt>おそ</rt></ruby>れ<ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;be astonished</span></span>。よくあんなものを<span class="vocab">食って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;eat</span></span>、あれだけに<span class="vocab">暴れられた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>暴</rb><rt>あば</rt></ruby>れられた&nbsp;be unruly; run amuck</span></span>もんだ。それで晩飯を<span class="vocab">急いで<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>急</rb><rt>いそ</rt></ruby>いで&nbsp;hurriedly</span></span><span class="vocab">四時半<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>四時半</rb><rt>よじはん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;4:30</span></span>に<span class="vocab">片付けて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>片付</rb><rt>かたづ</rt></ruby>けて&nbsp;finish up</span></span>しまうんだから<span class="vocab">豪傑<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>豪傑</rb><rt>ごうけつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;heroic; extraordinary</span></span><span class="vocab">に違いない<span class="vocabdef">に<ruby><rb>違</rb><rt>ちが</rt></ruby>いない&nbsp;without a doubt</span></span>。<span class="vocab">飯<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>飯</rb><rt>めし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;meal</span></span>は食ったが、まだ<span class="vocab">日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the sun</span></span>が<span class="vocab">暮れない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>暮</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>れない&nbsp;set; go down</span></span>から<span class="vocab">寝る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寝</rb><rt>ね</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;go to bed</span></span><span class="vocab">訳に行かない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>訳</rb><rt>わけ</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>かない&nbsp;can't do ...</span></span>。ちょっと<span class="vocab">温泉<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>温泉</rb><rt>おんせん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;onsen</span></span>に<span class="vocab">行きたく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>きたく&nbsp;want to go</span></span>なった。<span class="vocab">宿直<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿直</rb><rt>しゅくちょく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;night duty</span></span>をして、<span class="vocab">外へ出る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>外</rb><rt>そと</rt></ruby>へ<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;go out</span></span>のはいい<span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;act; fact</span></span>だか、<span class="vocab">悪るい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>悪</rb><rt>わ</rt></ruby>るい&nbsp;bad (not allowed)</span></span>事だかしらないが、こう<span class="vocab">つくねんと<span class="vocabdef">つくねんと&nbsp;vacantly; idly</span></span>して<span class="vocab">重禁錮<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>重禁錮</rb><rt>じゅうきんこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;imprisonment (with hard labor); close confinement</span></span><span class="vocab">同様<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同様</rb><rt>どうよう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;equivalent</span></span>な<span class="vocab">憂目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>憂目</rb><rt>うきめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;misery; suffering</span></span>に<span class="vocab">逢う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>逢</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;meet with; experience</span></span>のは<span class="vocab">我慢の出来る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>我慢</rb><rt>がまん</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;tolerable</span></span>もんじゃない。<span class="vocab">始めて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>めて&nbsp;the first time</span></span><span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the school</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">来た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;came (to)</span></span>時<span class="vocab">当直<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>当直</rb><rt>とうちょく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;on duty</span></span>の<span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;person</span></span>はと<span class="vocab">聞いたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>いたら&nbsp;inquired</span></span>、ちょっと<span class="vocab">用達<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>用達</rb><rt>ようたし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;errand</span></span>に<span class="vocab">出た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;went out</span></span>と<span class="vocab">小使<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>小使</rb><rt>こづかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;janitor</span></span>が<span class="vocab">答えた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>答</rb><rt>こた</rt></ruby>えた&nbsp;answered</span></span>のを<span class="vocab">妙<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>妙</rb><rt>みょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;odd; strange</span></span>だと<span class="vocab">思った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought</span></span>が、<span class="vocab">自分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;oneself</span></span>に<span class="vocab">番<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>番</rb><rt>ばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(one's) turn</span></span>が<span class="vocab">廻って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>廻</rb><rt>まわ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;come around</span></span>みると<span class="vocab">思い当る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>い<ruby><rb>当</rb><rt>あた</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;reconsider</span></span>。<span class="vocab">出る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;go out</span></span><span class="vocab">方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>ほう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;alternative; choice</span></span>が<span class="vocab">正しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>正</rb><rt>ただ</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;correct; right</span></span>のだ。おれは小使にちょっと出てくると云ったら、<span class="vocab">何か<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>か&nbsp;some (kind of)</span></span><span class="vocab">ご用<span class="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>用</rb><rt>よう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;business</span></span>ですかと聞くから、用じゃない、温泉へはいるんだと答えて、さっさと<span class="vocab">出掛けた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出掛</rb><rt>でか</rt></ruby>けた&nbsp;set out</span></span>。<span class="vocab">赤手拭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤手拭</rb><rt>あかてぬぐい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;red towel</span></span>は<span class="vocab">宿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿</rb><rt>やど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lodgings</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">忘れて来た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>忘</rb><rt>わす</rt></ruby>れて<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;left behind</span></span>のが<span class="vocab">残念<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>残念</rb><rt>ざんねん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;unfortunate</span></span>だが<span class="vocab">今日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today</span></span>は<span class="vocab">先方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先方</rb><rt>せんぽう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one's destination</span></span>で<span class="vocab">借りる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>借</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>りる&nbsp;borrow</span></span>としよう。</p>

